"        <a href=\"https://pouet.chapril.org/@tibillet\">Mastodon</a>.\n"
"    </p>\n"
"    <p>We hope you enjoy your time with us!</p>\n"
"    <p><a href=\"%(create_url_for_onboard_stripe)s\">\n"
