"        process &lt;-\n"
"    </a></p>\n"
"    </div>\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    <p>\n"
"        D'ici-là, vous pouvez nous contacter en passant par\n"
"        <a href=\"mailto:contact@tibillet.re\">notre mail de support</a> ou "
"sur <a  href=\"https://discord.gg/7FJvtYx\">Discord</a>,\n"
"        <a href=\"https://matrix.to/#/#tibillet:tiers-lieux.org\">Matrix</a> "
